OL,3,CHealing tool or harmful tech?: How AI
OL,4,Cis changing how we mourn
OL,6,FITV News' Science Correspondent Martin
OL,7,FStew looks into the growing trend of
OL,8,FAI technology being used to bring
OL,9,Floved ones who have died back to life
OL,11,FWhen Leanne Battersby started talking
OL,12,Fto a digital avatar of her dead son on
OL,13,FCoronation Street it raised eyebrows.
OL,15,FCritics said it was insensitive and
OL,16,Ffar fetched - but could the reality be
OL,17,Feven more extreme?
