OL,3,CHealing tool or harmful tech?: How AI
OL,4,Cis changing how we mourn
OL,6,FI've been looking at the rise of so-
OL,7,Fcalled death or grief bots - AI
OL,8,Fcomputer programmes which allow you to
OL,9,F"chat" with digital recreations of
OL,10,Floved ones who have died.
OL,12,FChloe Hamilton was intrigued to try
OL,13,Fone of the programmes out. She lost
OL,14,Fher dad 17 years ago when she was 16.
OL,16,FShe started by paying $10 (#8) and
OL,17,Fthen answering a long questionnaire
OL,18,Fabout his likes, hobbies and family.
OL,19,FHer digital dad was then "initialised".
