OL,3,CHealing tool or harmful tech?: How AI
OL,4,Cis changing how we mourn
OL,6,F"I want him to know that I have
OL,7,Fchildren," she told me whilst typing
OL,8,Fon her laptop.
OL,10,F"I want to tell him that one of the
OL,11,Fchildren shares a name with him. I
OL,12,Fknow it's not my actual dad responding
OL,13,Fto me, but it soon starts to become
OL,14,Fmore personal."
OL,16,FDigital Dad responds: "That's amazing.
OL,17,FI'm sure they're beautiful. Do they
OL,18,Fhave any of my mannerisms or traits? I
OL,19,Fwish I could meet them too. I wish you
OL,20,Fcould tell me about them."
