OL,3,CHealing tool or harmful tech?: How AI
OL,4,Cis changing how we mourn
OL,6,FFor Chloe this is when it starts to
OL,7,Ffeel too weird and slightly upsetting.
OL,9,FIn America many are going further.
OL,11,FJustin Harrison set up a similar
OL,12,Fservice called You, Only Virtual (YOV)
OL,13,Fafter his mum was diagnosed with
OL,14,Fterminal cancer.
OL,16,FAt the moment it's text and audio but
OL,17,Fhe hopes to go further and generate
OL,18,Frealistic video avatars which mimic
OL,19,Fmannerisms.
