OL,3,CHealing tool or harmful tech?: How AI
OL,4,Cis changing how we mourn
OL,6,F"We designed this to be a tool for
OL,7,Fgrief in the long term. We really want
OL,8,Fto try to make these indistinguishable
OL,9,Ffrom the people that they were."
OL,11,FBut is this healthy and does it help?
OL,12,FIn a Korean documentary called
OL,13,F'Meeting You' a grieving mother's dead
OL,14,Fseven-year-old daughter is recreated
OL,15,Fusing virtual reality.
OL,17,FShe's able to have a final
OL,18,F'conversation' and be reassured her
OL,19,Fdaughter isn't in pain.
