OL,3,CHealing tool or harmful tech?: How AI
OL,4,Cis changing how we mourn
OL,6,FBut is this simply delaying the
OL,7,Fgrieving process?
OL,9,FPsychologist Elaine Kasket says whilst
OL,10,Fgrief bots may help some, for others
OL,11,Fthey could prolong the pain.
OL,13,F"When we try to use technology to
OL,14,Fremove these hard experiences, it
OL,15,Fnever really works the way that we
OL,16,Ffantasise that it will, it can't take
OL,17,Faway our pain. It can't take away the
OL,18,Fsting of loss. And eventually maybe we
OL,19,Fget to the point where we realise
OL,20,Fthat's okay."
