OL,3,CHealing tool or harmful tech?: How AI
OL,4,Cis changing how we mourn
OL,6,FWhat about the ethical questions?
OL,8,FScientists at Cambridge University
OL,9,Fhave been considering who owns the
OL,10,Fdead's data.
OL,12,FWhat's to stop a malign actor from
OL,13,Fharvesting people's data from online,
OL,14,Fcreating an avatar and using it to
OL,15,Fadvertise to or influence others? How
OL,16,Fdo you protect the living as well?
