OL,3,CHealing tool or harmful tech?: How AI
OL,4,Cis changing how we mourn
OL,6,F"We already know that there are
OL,7,Fparents who are terminally ill who are
OL,8,Fdesigning or developing these dead
OL,9,Fbots for their children right now" say
OL,10,Fscientist Tomasz Hollanek . "Untill we
OL,11,Fknow that this effect is positive, we
OL,12,Fbelieve that this should not be
OL,13,Fallowed."
OL,15,FThe government is working on the
OL,16,FOnline Safety Act which will include
OL,17,FAI generated content.
OL,19,FThe challenge is legislation needing
OL,20,Fto keep up with a deathbot industry
OL,21,Fthat has has a life of its own.
